{"tid":2266082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"盧寵茂批港甩漏多　確診者留家等入院無稽：內地清零是良好示範","createTime":"2020-11-01T04:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T06:52:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"5c194bf19558d4853ca89577a0d307dcbe851451","tid":2266082,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:22:20.000Z","msg":"隨著本港疫情放緩，中港醞釀互認通關，香港大學深圳醫院院長盧寵茂今(1日)於商台「政好星期天」受訪時表示，經濟復蘇並無捷徑，他不同意人類要與病毒共存的說法，「我們應該係要同佢勢不兩立」，又指內地「清零」是對本港的良好示範。他又提到，本港處理疫情仍有不少「甩漏」，包括容許有病徵者「周街走」、病人確診後需留家等候入院多時的做法無稽。<br />\n<br />\n全國政協常委、醫管局前主席胡定旭則表示，深圳內循環強勁，倘今時今日不通關，對本港經濟有很大影響，他認為，本港只有「防外開內 」的一條出路，嚴格控制輸入個案的同時，需要承接國內經濟勢頭接軌。<br />\n<br />\n胡定旭表示，深圳已見回復常態，「深圳旺到不得了，內循環好強勁」，倘今時今日不通關，對本港經濟有很大影響，他認為，本港只有一條出路，應以「防外開內 」原則應對疫情，嚴格控制，輸入個案，另一方面要與內地接軌，「國內經濟好，唔去接上，會好傻」。<br />\n<br />\n不同意與病毒共存說法 應勢不兩立<br />\n身處深圳、正接受隔離的香港大學深圳醫院院長盧寵茂則表示，經濟復蘇並無捷徑，他不同意人類要與病毒共存的說法，「我們應該係要同佢勢不兩立」，他形容病毒不講道理，會一直隨人類互動蔓延，應以清零為目標。他又指，內地正好是良好示範，國內一旦發現有小規模爆發，市民、當地政府，以至全國民眾都會合作「撲火」。<br />\n<br />\n病人確診後需留家等候入院等做法無稽<br />\n至於應否強制檢測，盧寵茂認為，病人有權利，但在疫情下亦有義務，他指，以其深圳醫院為例，發燒個案會分流在醫院門口負責，有病徵者不可進入醫院範圍內，涉及懷疑個案亦需進行檢測。他認為，市民應不忘公民義務，「太強調自己權利，其實係剝奪緊其他人」；盧寵茂又指，本港處理疫情仍有不少「甩漏」，包括有病徵者仍容許「周街走」、因醫院未有病床提供，病人確診後需留家等候入院等做法無稽。他又提到，內地奉行「應檢必檢 」原則，「而唔係好似香港咁，應檢盡檢」，認為本港仍有不少改善空間。<br />\n<br />\n胡定旭則期望，可強制高危群組接受檢測，私家醫生發現病人有少許病徵、或感懷疑，亦應安排測試，他同意不少有病徵病人「周街走」的情況是大件事，他又提到，本港已擴大檢測量，以其任職董事長的華昇診斷中心為例，每日可測試3萬個通量，24小時內、甚至幾小時已可得出檢驗結果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5595563/org/64ec6e177a3d1b5e63ca06227f65b9d4.jpg/_xtX9ziDzsvcDUOSYJ5_SeUz9vLGYRzYsIs5abCLOWk?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5595563%2Forg%2F64ec6e177a3d1b5e63ca06227f65b9d4.jpg%2F_xtX9ziDzsvcDUOSYJ5_SeUz9vLGYRzYsIs5abCLOWk%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=67270d13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3037c820e9c79f04255b8d51adb45b72d827ffd6","tid":2266082,"uid":7043,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n真心建議D人死番上去住<br />\n香港仲撚差住黎把撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bbe901ade0aa5296c17e7a64a537feca32971a","tid":2266082,"uid":51271,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"你幾時去武漢?"},{"pid":"2c697675e9d5af2e7790935697e274c3120959dc","tid":2266082,"uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:24:25.000Z","msg":"BTW, 新疆爆緊喎，清乜鳩零?<br />\n<br />\n台灣就真係reset to zero勒"},{"pid":"a3fcc409c23468f6f530935076bcfdf711425f06","tid":2266082,"uid":91017,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"係人都知你鳩up吹牛, 你之前夠話親身上去幫助內地同胞, 到今日都未找數"},{"pid":"0e5ef34515e64ce23c11996c166850674a4ef482","tid":2266082,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3fcc409c23468f6f530935076bcfdf711425f06","tid":2266082,"uid":91017,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"係人都知你鳩up吹牛, 你之前夠話親身上去幫助內地同胞, 到今日都未找數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"就快一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39a87190af4a4d7affcb30aeb596cf03d3c433c","tid":2266082,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"佢幾時先死上去醫下新疆啲人？"},{"pid":"409a52fef43672788bfa21a773e5be5aee12f22c","tid":2266082,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"信支那清零嘅人腦細胞都清零<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dad91fa7649f884f57c8faefb9fdd9d67341e87","tid":2266082,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:35:09.000Z","msg":"叻啦叻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431eae8b15a33010e4c920d83eecd23cfdd908d9","tid":2266082,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"胡定旭表示，深圳已見回復常態，「深圳旺到不得了，內循環好強勁」，倘今時今日不通關，對本港經濟有很大影響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c359d305df1c15ce9d9a4df92879f64de4a28acd","tid":2266082,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:37:05.000Z","msg":"支那知你有病係鎖你大門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf54240cd463eefcf1448e6eb64008e9b3ada31c","tid":2266082,"uid":340221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"咁中聯辦宿舍果單冇源頭感染嘅 case 喺邊度嚟家？你老母臭閪仲話清零？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e424fd8f037c4ad2f7769dbc99a7afd7d13bef","tid":2266082,"uid":125194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:42:17.000Z","msg":"睇嚟佢去武漢呢件事<br />\n就好似陳同佳去台灣咁"},{"pid":"310ec88f3129de5f9164d98834ba35b7c3ebf22a","tid":2266082,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"香港唔係中國一部分？<br />\n點零確診？"},{"pid":"a998557089ccdbbdae6319cbaa0e7f20149e75b1","tid":2266082,"uid":54516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"支那內需（好撚僧叫內循環）勁？<br />\n之前10.1因為冇得去外國先焗住係國內消費咋。<br />\n工作上識D支那有生意或者設廠嘅人。<br />\n一個整嘢外銷去外國（主要歐美），7月見過香港寫字樓會計傾過下計。佢話歐美為咗避武肺擴散閂咗好多門市，生意差咗好多，深圳廠已經比高峰時期一千人左右少一半人。而加歐美單日確診日日創新高，英國又想封城，歐美疫情搞唔掂深圳廠停工都得。<br />\n有一個係做婚嫁生意，一個做床上用品，問佢哋生意如何已經唔想提。做廠嘅甚至有打算執咗間廠。"},{"pid":"50606aa0d85062b83dfc1daa5cf51b3c1d136f16","tid":2266082,"uid":31370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a7936f293f99ded2691bb3357f5b67eefe2ee4","tid":2266082,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我同意與病毒共存說法</span></span> 應該當係傷風/流感看待"},{"pid":"9cdf5002830a821259c7afea15c906d24b52e52b","tid":2266082,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:51:53.000Z","msg":"再次引入支那肺炎，都係想搞掂班支那廢老同藍屍啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a2dac2e0bb5e8b5246dc2e1376d0bea1b776e0","tid":2266082,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:52:03.000Z","msg":"青島唔係有爆發咩而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c611c63f0f6cb74c16b46ee41e77902f3725f38","tid":2266082,"uid":146427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"內地戲院門票都可以改名造假<br />\n<br />\n支共為左威威改病歷有幾咁奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蚛蟈係控制得好，因為控制左個消息嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n信蚛蟈都ON撚柒9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b858d11c32a577708446f71279b90fb2f544c1","tid":2266082,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:04:38.000Z","msg":"呢個時候就一國兩制<br />\n係你香港搞唔掂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0111e121f0ce2f5d0c0934ac3bf24c8996167706","tid":2266082,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"啱啱先有個支聯辦畜牲喺深圳瀨返嚟"},{"pid":"819e173122972a24764d662ae6fe963dd4e482e7","tid":2266082,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:05:5